item.title: NRL 360 - Grand Final recap, Kenty blasts the Panthers carry-on post victory! - 03/10/22
item.description:
Catch up on all the Rugby League news from NRL360, Monday the 3rd of October, with host Braith Anasta and of course, Paul Kent.

The boys are joined by Brent Reed and James Hooper to discuss the 2022 NRL Grand Final between the Penrith Panthers and the Parramatta Eels in the final episode of NRL 360 for the year.

For more of the show tune in on Fox League CH 502 or stream full episodes on KAYO.
